Criando a vlan:

    Interfaces > VLAN > Add

        New Interface
        
            General

                Name: vlan200-AZUL

                VLAN ID: 200

// Interface que vai para o switch. //
                
                Interface: eth6-SW

    IP > Addresses

        Addresses List > Add

            New Address

                Address: 10.200.200.1/24

                Interface: vlan200-AZUL

// Configurar o servidor DHCP na interface vlan200-AZUL. //

    IP > DHCP SERVER > DHCP Setup

// No switch vamos criar a bridge. //

    Bridge > Add

        General

            Name: bridge-LAN

// Adicionando as interfaces (uma por uma) que fazem parte da bridge. //

    Ports > Add

// Adicionando as interfaces da bridge na vlan que desejamos. //
// Acesse a interface.. //

    Bridge Port

        VLAN

            PVID: 200

    Bridge > VLANS > Add

        New Bridge VLAN

            Bridge: bridge-LAN

            VLAN IDs: 200

            Tagged: eth1-router

            Untagged:   eth8-pc4
                        eth9-pc3

    Bridge > bridge-LAN
        
        VLAN

            VLAN Filtering: enable
